OL,3,CQuestions over 'legality' of
OL,4,CBallycastle hotel demolition
OL,6,FA council is investigating the
OL,7,Flegality of the demolition of the
OL,8,Fformer Antrim Arms Hotel in
OL,9,FBallycastle.
OL,11,FThe structure situated in the town's
OL,12,FDiamond area was demolished in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of Thursday.
OL,15,FCordons have been in place around the
OL,16,Fbuilding for more than a year due to
OL,17,Fconcerns over its structural integrity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
