OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783720151
OL,3,CQuestions over 'legality' of
OL,4,CBallycastle hotel demolition
OL,6,FIn a statement, Causeway Coast and
OL,7,FGlens Borough Council said they were
OL,8,Faware that the building had been
OL,9,F"substantially demolished".
OL,11,F"Council officers will inspect the
OL,12,Fsite including investigating the
OL,13,Flegality of the demolition and
OL,14,Fliaising with the relevant
OL,15,Forganisations as appropriate.
OL,17,FAlliance MLA for North Antrim, Sian
OL,18,FMulholland described people in the
OL,19,Fcommunity will be ''deeply troubled''
OL,20,Fby the demolition.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
