OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783720151
OL,3,CQuestions over 'legality' of
OL,4,CBallycastle hotel demolition
OL,6,FShe said: ''It is heartbreaking to see
OL,7,Fan iconic piece of Ballycastle's built
OL,8,Fheritage reduced to a pile of rubble.
OL,10,F"A building that has stood on that
OL,11,Fsite for almost 200 years, and which
OL,12,Fholds a special place in the memory of
OL,13,Fso many from the north coast and
OL,14,Ffurther afield, is now gone."
OL,16,FIn April, more than 40 firefighters
OL,17,Fbattled a fire at the site which was
OL,18,Ftreated as deliberate.
